Oinker/Pyro/Punch/Zergling:


Pyro cursed, rolling out of the way of laser blasts.

---

Oinker fired off two bolts at Shadow Wing, each missing by a yard or 
two.



-----

Punch and Zergling entered the Ark.

---

Ramhorn came around a corner, firing off ten shells, five digging 
into Zergling's chest.

Punch fired his rocket, sending Ramhorn flying back several feet, 
smashing to the ground.

The two Alliance members continued.

----

They entered the CR chamber room.  There were a few CR chambers, so 
they had no idea which one to pick.

Zergling set a charge down in the middle of the room.  It would hit 
all the CR Chambers, but it might not kill whoever was inside.  They 
headed off, the charge down to 3 seconds.
